= direction of time =
====== short ======
What are the features which allow us to determine which direction in time is the
future and which is the past?
<br><br>
Why is entropy higher in future? Is increasing entropy definitional (i.e. the
future is whichever direction in time that entropy increases), due to an
asymmetry in physical laws (and which temporal direction is the future can be
determined with regard to that asymmetry) or something else?

